          <actionDate>2017-04-07</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Energy Workforce for the 21st Century Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish a comprehensive program to improve education and training for energy- and manufacturing-related jobs, with emphasis on increasing the number of skilled individuals from underrepresented groups trained to work in those jobs.</p>]]></text>
